Package: mgnet
Title: Network Analysis and Visualization for Metagenomics Communities
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
  person("Alessandro", "Fuschi", role = c("aut", "cre"), email="alessandro.fuschi.work@gmail.com")
Description: This package provides tools for constructing, analyzing, and visualizing networks of microbial community interactions. It integrates methods for data processing for compositional data and sparsity, network construction based on correlation and association measures, and advanced visualization capabilities to help researchers understand complex microbial relationships.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
